OL,3,C'I was left without pain relief for
OL,4,Ceight hours after having a caesarean'
OL,6,FA mother who had an emergency
OL,7,Fcaesarean birth said her husband had
OL,8,Fto bring her pain relief from home
OL,9,Fafter she was left for eight hours
OL,10,Fwithout it at a Swansea hospital.
OL,12,FHeather Davies, from Loughor, also
OL,13,Fsaid she wasn't seen by a doctor for
OL,14,Fthree days after giving birth at
OL,15,FSingleton Hospital.
OL,17,FThe mum-of-one gave birth to her son
OL,18,FFinley prematurely after eight rounds
OL,19,Fof IVF.
