OL,3,C'I was left without pain relief for
OL,4,Ceight hours after having a caesarean'
OL,6,FShe and her husband, Ceri, lost five
OL,7,Fbabies during previous pregnancies
OL,8,Fbefore Finley arrived at 34 weeks.
OL,10,FWhile she described her experience
OL,11,Fleading up to and during the birth as
OL,12,F"amazing", Heather said postnatal care
OL,13,Fat the hospital was "absolutely
OL,14,Fhorrendous".
OL,16,FHeather gave birth in June last year,
OL,17,Fbut results of an inspection in April
OL,18,Fthat were published on Tuesday
OL,19,Frevealed women were still facing
OL,20,Fdelays in getting pain relief.
