OL,3,C'I was left without pain relief for
OL,4,Ceight hours after having a caesarean'
OL,6,FIt follows a previous inspection of
OL,7,FSingleton Hospital in September, which
OL,8,Fruled the maternity unit as "unfit for
OL,9,Fpurpose" and highlighted the same
OL,10,Fdelays in pain relief administration.
OL,12,FThe Health Secretary Eluned Morgan
OL,13,Fplaced the unit under enhanced
OL,14,Fmonitoring and the health board
OL,15,Fcommissioned an independent review.
OL,17,FSince then "significant improvements"
OL,18,Fhave been made according to Tuesday's
OL,19,Freport, which praised hard-working
OL,20,Fstaff for trying to provide families
OL,21,Fwith a positive experience.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/12
