OL,4,Ceight hours after having a caesarean'
OL,6,FBut Heather said it was "unacceptable"
OL,7,Fthat women were still enduring some of
OL,8,Fthe issues she faced there over a year
OL,9,Fago.
OL,11,FSpeaking about her experience, Heather
OL,12,Fsaid: "I was really surprised because
OL,13,Fleading up to that it was all really
OL,14,Fpositive.
OL,16,F"The midwives were amazing, the
OL,17,Fdoctors that I saw in the antenatal
OL,18,Fclinic for check-ups were always
OL,19,Freassuring. It was all really positive
OL,20,Fup until I had him.
