OL,3,C'I was left without pain relief for
OL,4,Ceight hours after having a caesarean'
OL,6,F"He was already a miracle, and the
OL,7,Ffact that he was here was a miracle
OL,8,Fand I was worried and I wasn't getting
OL,9,Fany kind of help, empathy or
OL,10,Freassurance from them whatsoever.
OL,12,F"I had pain relief when I asked for
OL,13,Fit, but then when I was moved to my
OL,14,Fown room I was pressing the buzzer and
OL,15,Fnobody was coming. It was really bad
OL,16,Fand I was left eight hours without
OL,17,Fpain relief.
OL,19,F"After giving birth to be not given
OL,20,Fsufficient pain relief, I don't think
OL,21,Fthat's acceptable.
