OL,6,FShe also claimed staff said they were
OL,7,F"too busy" to take her to see Finley,
OL,8,Fwho had been taken straight to the
OL,9,Fneonatal intensive care unit (NICU)
OL,10,Ffollowing his birth.
OL,12,F"I wasn't able to get up and about so
OL,13,FI wasn't able to go and see him," she
OL,14,Fsaid.
OL,16,F"I phoned by husband crying and he
OL,17,Fended up driving down to the hospital
OL,18,Fso I could go and sit in the NICU with
OL,19,Fhim."
