OL,6,FDuring their visit in April,
OL,7,Finspectors were concerned about unsafe
OL,8,Fstaffing levels and found a lack of
OL,9,Fappropriate skill mix within the
OL,10,Fantenatal assessment unit.
OL,12,FMidwifery staff said they were not
OL,13,Falways able to access essential
OL,14,Fmedical equipment to provide
OL,15,Fsufficient care to patients.
