OL,6,FBut inspectors said there had been
OL,7,Fsignificant improvements in mandatory
OL,8,Ftraining, a stable leadership was
OL,9,Femerging, the unit was clean and free
OL,10,Fof clutter and there was effective
OL,11,Fteam-working.
OL,13,FSwansea Bay University Health Board,
OL,14,Fwhich oversees around 3,200 births a
OL,15,Fyear, said it is committed to
OL,16,Fcontinuously improving its maternity
OL,17,Fservices.
