OL,6,FIt added that it is taking firm action
OL,7,Fto meet all the recommendations and
OL,8,Fpointed out that maternal and neonatal
OL,9,Fdeath mortality rates are lower at
OL,10,FSingleton Hospital than in other
OL,11,Fsimilar services in the UK.
OL,13,FLlais, the independent body
OL,14,Frepresenting people receiving
OL,15,Fhealthcare in Wales, said it is
OL,16,F"concerned about the pace of change"
OL,17,Fat the maternity unit.
